org.cougaar.core.thread
Class DynamicSortedQueue<T extends Schedulable>

java.lang.Object
  org.cougaar.core.thread.DynamicSortedQueue<T>

public class DynamicSortedQueue<T extends Schedulable>
extends java.lang.Object

A simple queue, built on array list, that uses a Comparator to determine which elements is next (the smallest, according to the Comparator). Note that this is not a Collection. Also note that the methods are not synchronized. It's the caller's reponsibility to handle synchronization. Queues of this kind are used by Schedulers to hold Schedulables that are not able to run immediately.
